ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Repealing the United Nations Sierra Leone Regulations
PrecisRegulations repealing the UNITED NATIONS SIERRA LEONE REGULATIONS in order to remove the arms embargo on Sierra Leone and bring Canada in line with its own legislation and the international norm on sanctions against Sierra Leone.
